title=Database Query Builder: Connecting to an SQL Database
topics=<p>Key Topics Covered in this Tutorial:</p>\n<p>-&#9;When to use an SQL database instead of Revolution&#146;s built-in data storage</p>\n<p>-&#9;How to use the point and click Query Builder and some fields to create a simple front end to any popular SQL database</p>\n<p>-&#9;How to save changes to the database</p>\n<p></p>